    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows wear, and there is a small crack in the dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may eventually need minor suspension work and a new set of tires. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 19500.0,
